{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/cn/hymn/ch/134",
  "title": "你的大爱，过于人所能度",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "你 的"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "大"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "愛， 過"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "於 人"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "所 能 度，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "救 主"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "耶 穌！"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "但 不"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "堪 的 我，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "真 要 知"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "道 祂"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "的 高、 深、 長、"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "闊，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "好 叫 祂"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "的 能"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "力 越"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "顯 越"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "多"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "在"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "我"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "身"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "上！"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你的慈爱，过于人所能论，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我救主耶稣！但我的嘴唇"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "要向远近罪人劝诲谆谆，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "告诉他们，你爱能解忧困，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "并赐喜乐。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你的奇爱，过于人所能赞，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我救主耶稣！但我的心坎"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "总要歌唱那爱，这大！这满！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "因为恶性如我，也得恩湛，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "来亲近神！"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我今虽然不能在这地方"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "测度、讲论、颂赞爱的泱漭，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "但我要带我的虚空心房，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "来到你这爱的泉源良港，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "求你充满！"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我真是一个虚空的器皿，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "对你从无一次恋慕深情，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "但我却能一再来你面前，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "求你怜恤、帮助，得你恩典，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "因你爱我！"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "哦我主，求你用爱充满我，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "领我到天上永活的江河，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "让我用简单的信到那里，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "倚靠、鉴赏、称羡并享受你，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "不再他求。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "当我面对面看见我救主，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "当我在祂的宝座前俯伏，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "那时，我就要希奇并歌唱"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂的大爱如何深、高、阔、长，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "并要敬拜。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
